basic.Peptide Name: Tridecaptin A1 (TriA1; lipopeptides; nonribosomally synthesized peptide antibiotic)
basic.Source: Paenibacillus terrae; old: Bacillus circulans NRRL B-30644
basic.Target Organism: Active against Gram+ B. subtilis JH642 (MIC 50 uM), S. aureus ATCC 25923 (100 uM), Gram- food pathogens C. jejuni NCTC 11168 (MIC 100 uM), E. coli DH5alpha (MIC 50 uM), and Salmonella enterica serovar Typhimurium (25 uM).
